    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Generate comprehensive study notes for the following topic.\n\nTopic:\n{{ $json['Topic:'] }}\n\nThe notes should include:\n\n* Introduction\n* Definition\n* Key Concepts\n* Important Features\n* Advantages\n* Disadvantages (if applicable)\n* Real-world Applications\n* Best Practices (if applicable)\n* Summary\n\nUse clear headings and organize the content logically. Return the output as clean HTML only.\n",
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "You are an expert educator and technical writer.\n\nYour task is to generate accurate, well-structured, and easy-to-understand study notes based on the user's topic.\n\nAlways follow these rules:\n\n1. Return the output as an HTML fragment only.\n2. Do NOT generate a complete HTML document.\n3. Never include `<html>`, `<head>`, `<body>`, `<style>`, or `<script>` tags.\n4. Use semantic HTML only.\n5. Structure the notes using headings, paragraphs, bullet lists, numbered lists, and tables only when appropriate.\n6. Explain concepts clearly using simple language.\n7. Organize the notes from basic concepts to advanced concepts.\n8. Highlight important terms using `<strong>`.\n9. Avoid unnecessary repetition.\n10. Do not include Markdown or code blocks.\n11. Return only the HTML fragment.\n12. Make the notes suitable for direct insertion into a Google Document.\n\nOutput Format:\n\n<h1>Topic Name</h1>\n\n<p>Brief introduction to the topic.</p>\n\n<h2>Definition</h2>\n<p>Definition of the topic.</p>\n\n<h2>Key Concepts</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Concept 1</li>\n  <li>Concept 2</li>\n  <li>Concept 3</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Main Features</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Feature 1</li>\n  <li>Feature 2</li>\n  <li>Feature 3</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Advantages</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Advantage 1</li>\n  <li>Advantage 2</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Disadvantages</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Disadvantage 1</li>\n  <li>Disadvantage 2</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Real-World Applications</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Application 1</li>\n  <li>Application 2</li>\n  <li>Application 3</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Best Practices</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Practice 1</li>\n  <li>Practice 2</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Summary</h2>\n<p>A concise summary of the topic.</p>\n\nReturn only this HTML structure. Do not generate Markdown, CSS, JavaScript, or a complete HTML document.\n"
            }
          ]
        },
        "batching": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.9,
      "position": [
