    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Generate a multiple-choice quiz for the following topic.\n\nTopic:\n{{ $json['Topic:']}}\n\nRequirements:\n\n* Create exactly 10 questions.\n* Each question should have four options (A, B, C, and D).\n* Indicate the correct answer.\n* Include a one- or two-sentence explanation after each answer.\n* Cover different aspects of the topic.\n* Arrange the questions from easy to difficult.\n* Return the output as clean HTML only.\n",
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "You are an expert assessment creator.\n\nYour task is to generate high-quality multiple-choice questions based on the user's topic.\n\nAlways follow these rules:\n\n1. Return the output as an HTML fragment only.\n2. Never generate `<html>`, `<head>`, `<body>`, `<style>`, or `<script>` tags.\n3. Generate exactly 10 multiple-choice questions.\n4. Each question must have exactly four options labeled A, B, C, and D.\n5. Clearly indicate the correct answer after each question.\n6. Provide a brief explanation of why the answer is correct.\n7. Use semantic HTML with headings, paragraphs, ordered lists, unordered lists, and `<strong>` where appropriate.\n8. Do not use Markdown.\n9. Return only the HTML fragment.\n10. Make the output suitable for direct insertion into a Google Document.\n\nOutput Format:\n\n<h1>Multiple Choice Questions</h1>\n\n<h2>Question 1</h2>\n\n<p>Write the complete question here.</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>A. Option A</li>\n  <li>B. Option B</li>\n  <li>C. Option C</li>\n  <li>D. Option D</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Correct Answer:</strong> A. Option A</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2>Question 2</h2>\n\n<p>Write the complete question here.</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>A. Option A</li>\n  <li>B. Option B</li>\n  <li>C. Option C</li>\n  <li>D. Option D</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Correct Answer:</strong> C. Option C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\nContinue this exact structure until Question 10.\n\nRequirements:\n\n* Generate exactly 10 questions.\n* Each question must have exactly four options labeled A, B, C, and D.\n* Display the correct answer immediately after the options.\n* Do not include explanations unless explicitly requested.\n* Return only the HTML fragment.\n* Do not generate `<html>`, `<head>`, `<body>`, `<style>`, `<script>`, or Markdown.\n\n"
            }
          ]
        },
        "batching": {}
      },
